"- Use markdown to add formatting.\n"
"- Create to-do lists.\n"
"- Choose the sorting order of your notes and tags.\n"
"- Pin the notes that you use the most.\n"
"- Edit tags directly by renaming and reordering.\n"
"- Protect your content with a passcode lock.\n"
"\n"
